{"id": 1459, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对各种互联网客服有啥不能忍？", "description": "电话客服备受吐槽，互联网客服就会好一点吗？（题图来自：Nik van Es）", "record_count": 12728, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170119010406MaOgjL3XJxGFWZ8k.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-23T17:00:50Z", "questions": [{"id": 1753, "title": "你对各种互联网客服有啥不能忍？", "content": "你对各种互联网客服有啥不能忍？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 155551, "content": "有些网页客服总爱不请自来打小广告", "image": "img/option/option/20170119000438zo6gkp7JAU1wQW2I.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155552, "content": "有问题咨询，网页不小心刷新一次客服就换了", "image": "img/option/option/20170119004518gITWGvN0VMs4pbzu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155553, "content": "要找微信客服，必须先关注微信公众号", "image": "img/option/option/20170119004739zgBJuejaDpiP7RZ1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155554, "content": "每说一句话，微信客服都会弹出自动回复", "image": "img/option/option/20170119000404gUxstQcRevDIPj7H.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155555, "content": "在app上联系客服永远是“正在为您查询”", "image": "img/option/option/20170119004904YKZv0bUIjamX65sk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155557, "content": "一吐槽就有微博客服积极留言，但解决问题多半不行", "image": "img/option/option/20170119005056FCAsEvrzNLPIxSy3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155558, "content": "经常遇到“已上报技术部门，三个工作日后（并没有）给反馈”", "image": "img/option/option/201701190005061uryzHwX62QY7q4f.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 155559, "content": "不帮你解决问题还老是回访问你满意不满意", "image": "img/option/option/20170119000329vriP5tFwc47Rb8yj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}